298
00:22:09,895 --> 00:22:11,897
Like last night, this
system may develop

299
00:22:11,931 --> 00:22:14,366
into a storm of
detonating clay as well.

300
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:16,602
So keep that in mind
as you plan your day.

301
00:22:16,635 --> 00:22:18,470
You might want to store
your favorite puppets

302
00:22:18,504 --> 00:22:21,507
inside scrolls, and don't
forget your umbrella.

303
00:22:21,540 --> 00:22:25,778
Well, that's it for today's
Sand Village Accuweather Report.

304
00:22:25,811 --> 00:22:27,680
NARUTO (VOICEOVER): Next
time-- Run, Kankuro!

305
00:22:42,928 --> 00:22:44,530
-Today we're going
to be taking a look

306
00:22:44,563 --> 00:22:48,634
at the very important jobs
for ninja known as missions.

307
00:22:48,667 --> 00:22:51,670
The village receives mission
requests on a daily basis.

308
00:22:51,704 --> 00:22:56,675
Anything from finding lost pets
to escorting big-shot VIPS.

309
00:22:56,709 --> 00:22:58,310
Missions are broken
into five ranks

310
00:22:58,344 --> 00:22:59,879
according to the
level of difficulty,

311
00:22:59,912 --> 00:23:03,983
and are assigned to each
shinobi based on their ability.

312
00:23:04,016 --> 00:23:06,852
If the shinobi succeeds
and completes the mission,

313
00:23:06,886 --> 00:23:08,153
the village will earn a reward.

314
00:23:11,790 --> 00:23:13,726
For the most part,
missions are carried out

315
00:23:13,759 --> 00:23:17,029
in three man squads, units of
three ninja whose leader is

316
00:23:17,062 --> 00:23:18,464
of chunin rank or higher.

317
00:23:18,497 --> 00:23:20,766
This is the ideal
number of team members

318
00:23:20,799 --> 00:23:23,469
to carry out a mission
covertly and swiftly.

319
00:23:29,608 --> 00:23:30,409
Hey.

320
00:23:30,442 --> 00:23:31,877
Wait that's way too many people.

321
00:23:31,911 --> 00:23:34,947
This mission isn't gonna-- What?

322
00:23:34,980 --> 00:23:36,582
Whoa!

